name: Vintage and Pulp
description:
Stable-Diffusion v1.5 fine-tuned for 10k steps upon a blip captioned dataset of vintage images, then it underwent further fine tuning with dreambooth using the same dataset but rather then having it blip-captioned, it was split into "Vintage style", "Vintage face" and "Pulp cover" concepts

The model card and link to the dataset are available on Huggingface

modelVersions.name: SD15
modelVersions.description: This version was first fined-tuned on the whole dataset and only then it was fine-tuned again to learn each individual concept, so you can use it even without Trigger-Words and still get a subtle "Vintage" touch
